T1  - AN EQUILIBRIUM SEARCH MODEL OF SYNCHRONIZED SALES*
AU  - Albrecht, James
AU  - Postel-Vinay, Fabien
AU  - Vroman, Susan
Y1  - 2013/05/01
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12003
T2  - International Economic Review
