T1  - LAND USE REGULATION AS A BARRIER TO ENTRY: EVIDENCE FROM THE TEXAS LODGING INDUSTRY*
AU  - Suzuki, Junichi
Y1  - 2013/05/01
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12004
T2  - International Economic Review
